This rule provides standards for frontend components:

When working in components directory:

- Never use Tailwind for styling
- Use Framer Motion for animations
- Follow component naming conventions

This rule enforces validation for API endpoints:

In API directory:

- Use zod for all validation
- Define return types with zod schemas
- Export types generated from schemas

This rule enforces naming convention:

In components directrory:

components/
├── user-profile.tsx
├── data-table.tsx
└── navigation-bar.tsx

